---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Celsius">
  <div class="celsius-hero">
    <div class="celsius-hero-inner">
      <div class="celsius-badge">Myndform dreifir</div>
      <div class="celsius-logo">°C CELSIUS</div>
      <div class="celsius-tagline">LIVE FIT</div>
      <h1>Orkudrykkurinn<br>sem þrýtur af<br>náttúrulegum<br>innihaldsefnum.</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="intro-block">
      <div class="intro-text">
        <h2>Celsius orkudrykkur</h2>
        <p>Það er ekki að ástæðulausu að Celsius sé einn vinsælasti drykkur sinnar tegundar í Bandaríkjunum og á Norðurlöndunum. Margt íþróttafólk velur að svala þorstanum með Celsius þar sem drykkurinn inniheldur 114 mg af koffíni og er algjörlega kolvetnalaus. Celsius er einnig 100% vegan.</p>
        <p>Ásamt því að vera góð uppspretta koffíns inniheldur drykkurinn grænt te, króm, kalk, engifer og ýmis vel valin vítamín sem vinna í sameiningu að aukinni brennslu líkamans.</p>
        <p>Celsius er algjörlega sykurlaus, stútfullur af hollustu og inniheldur hver dos aðeins 4 hitaeiningar. Það verður enginn svikinn af Celsius!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-cans">
        <div class="cans-placeholder">
          <div class="can c1"></div>
          <div class="can c2"></div>
          <div class="can c3"></div>
          <div class="can c4"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flavours">
      <div class="flavours-label">Bragðtegundir</div>
      <div class="flavour-grid">
        <div class="flavour-card f1">
          <div class="flavour-name">Peach Vibe</div>
          <div class="flavour-type">Sparkling</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flavour-card f2">
          <div class="flavour-name">Strawberry Lemonade</div>
          <div class="flavour-type">Sparkling</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flavour-card f3">
          <div class="flavour-name">Fantasy Vibe</div>
          <div class="flavour-type">Sparkling · Nýtt</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flavour-card f4">
          <div class="flavour-name">Cosmic Vibe</div>
          <div class="flavour-type">Sparkling</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="facts-grid">
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-number">114mg</div>
        <div class="fact-label">Koffín á dós</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-number">4</div>
        <div class="fact-label">Hitaeiningar</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-number">0g</div>
        <div class="fact-label">Sykur</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-number">100%</div>
        <div class="fact-label">Vegan</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="celsius-cta">
    <div class="celsius-cta-inner">
      <div class="celsius-cta-title">Hefur þú áhuga á að selja Celsius?</div>
      <div class="celsius-cta-sub">Myndform dreifir Celsius til verslana um allt land — hafðu samband.</div>
      <a href="mailto:myndform@myndform.is" class="celsius-cta-btn">Hafðu samband</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ── HERO ── */
  .celsius-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #ea580c 50%, #c2410c 100%);
    padding: 72px 32px 80px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .celsius-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  .celsius-hero-inner { position: relative; max-width: 600px; }
  .celsius-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase; padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .celsius-logo {
    font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .celsius-tagline {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 42px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  /* ── CONTENT ── */
  .content { padding: 56px 32px 0; }

  .intro-block {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 56px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 56px;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .intro-text p {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-60); line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .intro-text p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* placeholder cans */
  .cans-placeholder {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 8px;
    justify-content: center; padding: 24px;
    background: var(--gray-10); border-radius: 12px;
    height: 240px;
  }
  .can {
    width: 52px; border-radius: 6px 6px 4px 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .c1 { height: 160px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fb923c, #ea580c); }
  .c2 { height: 180px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f43f5e, #e11d48); }
  .c3 { height: 200px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #a78bfa, #7c3aed); }
  .c4 { height: 170px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #38bdf8, #0284c7); }

  /* ── FLAVOURS ── */
  .flavours { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .flavours-label {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .flavour-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 12px;
  }
  .flavour-card {
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px 20px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .f1 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fb923c, #f97316); }
  .f2 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f43f5e, #e11d48); }
  .f3 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa, #7c3aed); }
  .f4 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8, #0284c7); }
  .flavour-name {
    font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 4px; line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .flavour-type {
    font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* ── FACTS ── */
  .facts-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 56px;
  }
  .fact-card {
    background: var(--gray-10); border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 28px 20px; text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #f97316;
  }
  .fact-number {
    font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 6px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .fact-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-60); font-weight: 500; }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .celsius-cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #ea580c);
    padding: 48px 32px;
  }
  .celsius-cta-inner { max-width: 560px; }
  .celsius-cta-title {
    font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .celsius-cta-sub {
    font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .celsius-cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--white); color: #ea580c;
    padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }
  .celsius-cta-btn:hover { opacity: 0.9; }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .celsius-hero { padding: 48px 20px 56px; }
    h1 { font-size: 30px; }
    .content { padding: 40px 20px 0; }
    .intro-block { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    .flavour-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .facts-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .celsius-cta { padding: 40px 20px; }
  }
</style>